      <title>美国机构称普京没有下令处决纳瓦尔尼：《华尔街日报》</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-27/us-agencies-say-putin-didn-t-order-navalny-s-february-death-wsj</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据《华尔街日报》报道，美国情报机构发现，俄罗斯总统弗拉基米尔·普京很可能没有下令在二月份的战俘营处决反对派领导人阿列克谢·纳瓦尔尼。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-27/us-agencies-say-putin-didn-t-order-navalny-s-february-death-wsj</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 04:30:53 GMT</pubDate>
