      <title>新加坡计划立法支持零工工人的退休需求</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-27/singapore-plans-law-to-support-gig-workers-retirement-needs</link>
      <description><![CDATA[新加坡人力部长陈思令表示，新加坡今年将出台一项新法律，帮助所谓的零工经济工人规划退休需求并获得工伤保护。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-27/singapore-plans-law-to-support-gig-workers-retirement-needs</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 27 Apr 2024 01:57:59 GMT</pubDate>
