      <title>在公众强烈反对后，不列颠哥伦比亚省取消毒品合法化</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/british-columbia-rolls-back-drug-decriminalization-after-public-backlash</link>
      <description><![CDATA[不列颠哥伦比亚省已要求加拿大政府重新实施公共场所吸毒禁令，这是一项有争议的将持有某些非法毒品合法化的实验的重大倒退。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-26/british-columbia-rolls-back-drug-decriminalization-after-public-backlash</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 26 Apr 2024 20:37:28 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
